Subject: RE: Estimated Ship Date/Tracking Questions Request Sold To: CIL Management Consultants Inc. Order #: 0338024807
BodyText:
Hi BB team,

 

VPO 37701995

 

Can you pls add these instructions for delivery ?

 

The Prudential Tower requires a Certificate of Insurance as well as a delivery date/ window. Deliveries made during regular business hours (6a-6p CT) need to be kept to under 30 minutes. If this delivery will take longer than 30 minutes, please let me know and we can arrange a time after 6p CT with a freight. Sample COI is attached – please let me know if you have any questions! I will forward the COI onto the building for approval.

 

 

Thanks
